    <item>
      <title>因争议，马里威胁让巴里克采矿许可证失效</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/mali-threatens-to-let-barrick-mine-permit-lapse-over-dispute</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在有关如何分配马里金矿经济利益的争议不断升级之际，马里军政府威胁要在 2026 年现有许可证到期时收回巴里克黄金公司 (Barrick Gold Corp.) 的 Loulo 矿特许权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/mali-threatens-to-let-barrick-mine-permit-lapse-over-dispute</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 18:15:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰抨击联合国秘书长与普京握手、与白俄罗斯拥抱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/ukraine-turns-on-un-chief-after-putin-handshake-and-belarus-hug</link>
      <description><![CDATA[安东尼奥·古特雷斯也许有理由后悔与面带微笑的弗拉基米尔·普京尴尬的握手、与白俄罗斯领导人亚历山大·卢卡申科的拥抱，甚至后悔决定在俄罗斯领土上参加金砖国家峰会。乌克兰人对此非常愤怒，并撤回了访问邀请。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/ukraine-turns-on-un-chief-after-putin-handshake-and-belarus-hug</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 18:12:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
